title: What kind of font is this? cant figure it out
author: NelsonG1122

comments.content: This is [Levi Brush](http://web.archive.org/web/20140724115913/http:/www.dafont.com/levibrush.font?fpp=100&psize=l&text=ROOM+630), and you can find these Brush and Graffiti scripts on dafont.com and many other free font websites.
